Summary: Was going through some pics I took last year and seen a object in the sky
divs: Sighting DetailsI take pictures sometimes of clouds when a storm comes in or when the sky looks unusual for screen savers for my computer . Was zooming in on some pics I took in the summer and had to send this one in .It shows a vehicle in the sky just above the house ,didn't know it was there till I zoomed in on it with windows picture viewer .It looked like it has a couple of different lighting features. I thought maybe a plane but it doesn't look like a plane to me .You are going to have to zoom in just above the roof in the center of the pic to see it.
